  danceClassesHub_whichCategory_combine_title: 'Can I combine several categories?',
  danceClassesHub_whichCategory_combine_text:
    "Absolutely! Many of our students combine classical technique (ballet/contemporary) with urban (dancehall/k-pop) or add physical training (bum bum/stretching) to their dance classes. It's the best way to develop as a complete dancer. Check our combined packages.",

  danceClassesHub_whichCategory_schedule_title: 'How to choose my ideal schedule?',
