  // FAQ - Location question
  classesFaqQ9: 'Where are the dance classes located in Barcelona?',
  classesFaqA9:
    'We are in the heart of Barcelona, near Plaça Catalunya, with direct access from Metro L1 (Sant Antoni / Universitat) and L2 (Universitat). Our exact address is Carrer de Floridablanca 135, Barcelona. Very accessible from the neighborhoods of Raval, Eixample, Gràcia, Sant Antoni and Ciutat Vella. Professional facilities with spacious rooms, dance floor and all the necessary equipment.',

  classesFaqQ6: "Where is Farray's Center located and how do I get there?",
  classesFaqA6:
    'We are located at Calle Entença 100, Barcelona 08015, in the Sants neighborhood. We are easily accessible by metro (L3/L5 - Sants Estació, L1 - Hostafrancs), bus (lines 27, 43, 78, 109, H10), or Renfe Cercanías (Sants Station). The studio is just a 5-7 minute walk from Sants station. There is also public parking nearby if you come by car.',
