    'Exclusive training system created by Yunaisy Farray, Street Dance 2 dancer and internationally recognized master. Combines specific physical preparation for dancers with injury prevention techniques and performance optimization. Fast and safe results.',

  prepFisica_why_specialized_title: 'Specialized Training for Dancers',
