    "Some look for a dance school similar to the ones they already know, and there's nothing wrong with that. And some look for the school they always dreamed of. At Farray's we belong to this second group.",
  about_story_p2:
    "But since this school didn't exist in Barcelona yet, we decided to create it and it's working. Since we didn't know it was impossible, we did it. We didn't know it was impossible to build it in a space abandoned for 10 years. We didn't know it was a bad idea to renovate it by hand, without budget, just Yunaisy, Fábio, friends, teachers and an improvised crew. We knew nothing about \"the impossible\". So we simply did it.",
  about_story_p3:
    "Farray's International Dance Center, more than a project, is a dream. A dream made reality by Cuban international dancer Yunaisy Farray. Considered one of the greatest references in Cuban female dance and one of the best dancers in the international scene, at the peak of her artistic and professional career she decides to take a step forward in her life: open a large dance center in the city she fell in love with, Barcelona.",
  about_story_highlight:
    "Because Farray's wasn't born from a business plan: it was born from a love story. From the love between Yunaisy and Fábio, from the love for dance and from the love for people.",

  // Vision Section
  about_vision_title: "Yunaisy's Vision",
  about_vision_p1:
    "From its origin, Farray's International Dance Center was born with a clear vocation: not just to be a dance school, but a sports and artistic club with a social integrating role, where dance, sports and culture are used as tools to improve society, promoting a healthy lifestyle and the physical, mental and emotional wellbeing of people in its community.",
  about_vision_p2:
    'Yunaisy set out to create a space that not only offers classes in many types of dance, but brings together a multitude of disciplines with a common goal: to nourish and care for the body and soul of all people who come to it.',
  about_vision_p3:
    "After two years tirelessly touring every corner of Barcelona searching for a place that could house a project of such magnitude, in 2017 the ideal space for Farray's Center went from being a dream to becoming reality.",

  // Today's Farray's Section
  about_today_title: "Farray's Today",
  about_today_intro:
    "Today, Farray's International Dance Center is a space of over 700 m² in the heart of Barcelona where dance classes for all levels, technical training, physical preparation, competition development, wellness activities and artistic projects coexist.",
  about_stat_space: 'of space in Barcelona',
  about_stat_active_students: 'active students',
  about_stat_total_students: 'students in 8 years',
  about_today_description:
    'It currently has more than 1500 active students and in just 8 years, more than 15,000 students have passed through its studios, consolidating it as one of the reference centers for dance in Barcelona.',

  // Mission Section
  about_mission_title: 'Our Mission',
  about_mission_p1:
    'This center pursues, as main objectives, on one hand, to promote sports and movement through dance and provide services that allow complete care of body and soul and, on the other, to generate opportunities and make the dreams of those who aspire to dance, grow and express themselves come true.',
  about_mission_p2:
    "Participating in competitions and training world-class dancers and artists of all ages is one of Farray's Center's priorities, but so is accompanying people who simply want to improve their physical and mental health through dance.",
  about_mission_highlight:
    'Dance is much more than a discipline or an art, it is the way we connect with our body, reconnect with our deepest feelings and with the true essence of our being.',

  // Social Impact Section
  about_social_title: 'Our Social Commitment',
  about_social_p1:
    "The activities carried out at Farray's are not limited to being lucrative activities, but have a marked integrating and social component, helping special sectors of the community such as abused women, incarcerated women, children and the elderly to reconnect with themselves and nourish their soul through dance.",
  about_social_p2:
    'Dance is the most ancestral form of communication —not only with others but with ourselves— and despite human evolution, it continues to remain within each of us waiting for someone to ignite that flame and teach us to keep it always alive.',

  // Values Section
  about_values_title: 'Our Values',
  about_values_intro:
    "The principles that guide every decision, every class and every moment at Farray's Center",

  about_value_love_title: 'Love for Dance',
  about_value_love_content:
    "Everything we do is born from love: love between people, love for dance and love for our community. It's not a slogan, it's our reality.",

  about_value_community_title: 'Family and Community',
  about_value_community_content:
    "Here you breathe family because that's how we build it. Every student, teacher and visitor is part of a unique community in Barcelona.",

  about_value_wellbeing_title: 'Integral Wellbeing',
  about_value_wellbeing_content:
    'We offer varied services aimed at a common goal: the complete physical, mental and emotional wellbeing of all people who come to us.',

  about_value_opportunities_title: 'Generation of Opportunities',
  about_value_opportunities_content:
    'We make the dreams of those who aspire to dance, grow and express themselves come true, training world-class dancers and artists of all ages.',

  about_value_social_title: 'Social Integration',
  about_value_social_content:
    'We help special sectors of the community reconnect with themselves through dance, with a marked integrating and social component.',

  about_value_excellence_title: 'Excellence and Professionalism',
  about_value_excellence_content:
    'Farray Method® created by Yunaisy Farray (dancer from Street Dance 2) and teachers trained in prestigious international schools guarantee the highest quality.',

  // Closing Statement
  about_closing_statement:
    'Yunaisy Farray and her team do precisely that: they ignite a flame of light, health and hope in each person who passes through her school, contributing to making society have people who are more physically and mentally healthy, more balanced, with more control over themselves and their emotions.',
  about_closing_tagline: 'In short, happier people.',

  // Final CTA
