  particularesPage_faqTitle: 'Frequently Asked Questions',
  particularesPage_faqQ1: 'Is previous experience necessary to take private classes?',
  particularesPage_faqA1:
    'No. Private classes are ideal for both beginners and advanced dancers. We adapt the content 100% to your level and goals.',
  particularesPage_faqQ2: 'Can I take private classes in any dance style?',
  particularesPage_faqA2:
    "Yes. We offer private classes in Salsa, Bachata, Dancehall, Contemporary Dance and other styles. When booking, tell us your interest and we'll assign you the perfect teacher.",
  particularesPage_faqQ3: 'Can I take private classes as a couple?',
  particularesPage_faqA3:
    "Of course. The price of the private class is the same whether it's individual or for a couple (2 people). Ideal for preparing for weddings, events or simply learning together.",
  particularesPage_faqQ4: 'How far in advance should I book my private class?',
  particularesPage_faqA4:
    'We recommend booking at least 48-72 hours in advance to ensure availability. Holders of the 10-class pack have scheduling priority.',
  particularesPage_faqQ5: 'How long are the class packs valid?',
  particularesPage_faqA5:
    'The 1-class pack has no expiration. The 5-class pack is valid for 3 months from purchase. The 10-class pack is valid for 6 months.',
  particularesPage_faqQ6: 'Can I cancel or reschedule a private class?',
  particularesPage_faqA6:
    'Yes. If you notify us 24 hours in advance, you can reschedule without problems. Cancellations with less notice forfeit the class.',
  particularesPage_faqQ7: 'Is it better to start with private classes or Premium classes?',
  particularesPage_faqA7:
    'It depends on your goals. If you have a specific goal (event, audition, limited time), private classes are ideal. If you seek continuous learning, technique and connection with other dancers, Premium classes offer excellent value.',

  particularesPage_ctaTitle: 'Ready to Take Your Dancing to the Next Level?',
  particularesPage_ctaText:
    'Book your private class now and start seeing results from day one. Personalized teaching, total dedication and guaranteed results.',
  particularesPage_ctaButton: 'Reserve Your First Class',
  particularesPage_ctaSecondary: 'I Have a Question',

  // What to Expect Section
  particularesPage_whatToExpect_title: 'What to Expect from Your Private Dance Classes?',
  particularesPage_whatToExpect_p1:
    "At Farray's International Dance Center, our private dance classes are designed to maximize your progress in the shortest time possible. Each 60-minute session is 100% personalized: your teacher dedicates full attention to correcting your technique, adapting the pace to your level, and focusing on your specific goals—whether mastering a style, preparing for a performance, or simply gaining confidence on the dance floor.",
  particularesPage_whatToExpect_p2:
    "Unlike regular group classes where the teacher must divide attention among 15-20 students, in private classes you are the sole focus. This means you'll learn 3 to 4 times faster: in a single private class you advance what would normally take 3-4 group classes. It's the most efficient way to learn to dance, especially if you have complicated schedules, ambitious goals, or simply value your time.",
  particularesPage_whatToExpect_p3:
    'Our teachers are highly qualified in over 25 dance styles: from Cuban Salsa, Bachata and Kizomba to Hip Hop, Dancehall, Contemporary and Ballet. You can choose to focus on a single style or combine several according to your interests. Additionally, we offer total flexibility: choose schedules that fit your agenda (mornings, afternoons, weekends), record your classes to review at home, and decide whether you prefer in-person classes at our Barcelona center, online via Zoom, or even at your home.',

  // Why Choose Section
  particularesPage_whyChoose_title: "Why Choose Farray's Center For Your Private Classes?",
  particularesPage_whyChoose_p1:
    'With over 8 years of experience training professional and amateur dancers, Farray\'s International Dance Center is the reference dance academy in Barcelona. Our team of teachers consists of active professional dancers, many with international careers, who master the revolutionary "Farray Method®": a unique methodology that combines classical technique, contemporary creativity and modern pedagogy to accelerate your learning.',
  particularesPage_whyChoose_p2:
    'Furthermore, we are the only dance center in Barcelona accredited by CID-UNESCO (International Dance Council), which guarantees world-class teaching standards. Our facilities feature studios equipped with professional mirrors, specialized wooden floors for dance, high-quality audio systems and climate-controlled spaces for your maximum comfort.',
  particularesPage_whyChoose_p3:
    "Whether you're looking to prepare for an audition, improve your technique, learn complex choreographies, or simply enjoy dancing in a safe and professional environment, our private classes are designed to help you achieve your specific goals. Total flexibility, proven results, and the experience of learning with Barcelona's best professionals.",

