  particularesPage_finalCta_description:
    'Private dance classes in Barcelona tailored to help you truly advance at your own pace. We work 100% focused on your goals with the Farray® Method: Cuban salsa, bachata, dancehall, hip hop, reggaeton, classical ballet, contemporary dance and more, led by Yunaisy Farray (dancer from Street Dance 2) and certified and experienced teachers. More than 8 years of experience in the heart of Barcelona.',
